##Fudan "new pneumonia prevention and control first lesson" , Zhang Wenhong said what

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

Reporter trainee, Zhang Hui, reporter, Sun Yizhen

"New pneumonia prevention and control of the first lesson" in the B station live broadcast of the value of hundreds of thousands of people. Video Source: Fudan University, edited by Yinzi Zeng at 39:59

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Screen grab from the live feed room

February 24 at 10:00 am, Fudan University to open the "new pneumonia prevention and control first class" officially launched, live broadcast in the B station of the value of hundreds of thousands of people.

"today is the first lesson of the beginning of school, but today is so special, AH, said the first lesson, I can not give you lessons in the classroom, I am the teacher of the Fudan University Shanghai Medical College. " After the class, Zhang Wenhong and everyone like this call.

He said he had come "out of his busy schedule" to record the course, "You must be wondering why there are so many people coming in from their busy schedules, right? I'm the busy one because we're doctors. "

“
It's not just you

“

It's not just you

Recently, Zhang Wenhong said to people starting work, "colleagues of fire prevention and theft prevention. " Facing his classmates, he still said in his usual tone, "Once school starts, you'll know what I want you to do. You do these things well, and nothing happens. If you don't do them well, it's not just your job. All your classmates will be affected. "

“
Guys, masks, please

Guys, masks, please

"Why do I wear a mask when I teach? I'll show you. On this Special Day, I beg you to wear a mask, " Zhang said, wearing a mask throughout the lecture

“
What are the symptoms in case of illness?

What are the symptoms in case of illness?

Fever is the most common symptom in mild cases, as well as coughing, sore throat, chest tightness and weakness, Zhang said. In addition, some patients experience nausea and vomiting, diarrhea, red eyes, and muscle soreness, the same symptoms as a cold. And very serious, it's pneumonia.

Critical illness is the elderly, people with basic diseases and obesity. "It's not as severe in young people, but the pneumonia itself is so severe that you can't breathe. "

“
Less words, more thoughts

Less words, more thoughts

Half the battle, everyone's at risk. What do we do?

"We have reached a new level. In Shanghai, we have very good control and the infection rate is very low. " Zhang Wenhong repeated the phrase "boring" . He suggested that students should be bored at home, bored at school, bored for two weeks, and take an online course. "You're not sick after two Mondays, and I tell you, congratulations, you're really not sick. "

What should students do in the dormitory? Zhang Wenhong said: "As long as we are bored for two weeks, less talking, you know, less language, thinking out. So, bored for two weeks to the majority of college students, is a good exercise Oh. "

He also reminded the students to do two things: First, after returning to Shanghai, in the dormitory honestly, do not dart around; second, stay alone. "If two people stay in the dormitory, it's OK, things separate, wear a mask, ok? When eating, don't get together to eat, eat your own OK? "

He said to his classmates, "you're not a doctor, but what you do is more important than a doctor. "

"The control of a disease is never a matter of doctors controlling it, " he stressed. "It's a matter of very effective prevention strategies. "

At the end of the course, a handwritten message from Zhang Wenhong reads, "winter is coming, spring is coming, mountains and rivers are safe, and the world is safe. ".
